description: The story is that, before the apocalypse, the scientists working on this project were told to stop because people were catching wind of the project. However, some scientists were too invested and kept secretly coming to the lab and working on it. One of those scientists ended up getting recruited by Earth First. The rogue scientists finally finished the Biomass Reactor but then the apocalypse happened. The one researcher from earth first died in the apocalypse so the Biomass reactor was still left there, running and powering the Lab.
author: John McCarthy
